235
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,640
You little brat!

236
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:45,976
- You brat!
- Mom, don't hit me.

237
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,280
- I'll hit you.
- I'm sorry, Mom!

238
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,376
- You hit her?
- You

239
