251
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:19,040
Mom, mom.

252
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:20,576
Mom.

253
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,880
- You okay?
- What happened, mom?

254
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,896
Mom.

255
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:25,040
