00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:10,697
You hurt someone,

279
00:14:10,721 --> 00:14:11,880
and still act this defiant?

280
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,296
Even your late father

281
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:16,520
would feel ashamed to
have a daughter like you!

282
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:18,096
The ashamed one should be you!

283
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,216
Doing anything

284
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,696
for my shares.

285
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,896
Like father, like son.

286
00:14:22,920 --> 00:14:24,336
Had both parents,

287
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:26,960
and still ended up with
a scumbag like Ti Cha!

288
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:27,800
You...

289
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:28,857
Fine.

290
00:14:28,881 --> 00:14:30,896
You won't yield until you see the coffin.

291
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:32,456
If you can't prove your innocence,

292
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,896
I'll carry out the family punishment.

293
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:34,920
Bring it.

294
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,536
I have

295
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:45,560
the evidence here.

296
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,320
My stomach hurts so much.

297
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:03,440
Anything else you want to say?

298
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:06,120
Without this video,

299
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,840
I'd be the one taking the blame.

300
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,640
Th... this video is edited.

301
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,880
You all teamed up to frame me.

302
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,000
Mom.

303
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,480
Please, take it slow.

304
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:23,016
I'm fine now.

305
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,136
The baby comes first.

306
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:25,720
Alright, forget it.

307
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:29,176
Good thing you're okay.

308
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,136
I'm just clumsy from pregnancy,

309
00:15:31,160 --> 00:15:32,816
so I slipped and knocked into you.

310
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,240
I swear, I didn't mean to do it.

