From now on,

313
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,400
I'll bear more heirs
for the Song family as compensation.

314
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,000
Alright.

315
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:44,000
So feudal-minded you don't even
care about your own life.

316
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:46,160
You truly deserve all this suffering.

317
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:18,416
